<i>Forever</i>

01:49:50.292 --> 01:49:52.876
<i>For always</i>

01:49:52.919 --> 01:49:55.921
<i>And more</i>

01:50:02.637 --> 01:50:06.432
<i>After this blackbird</i>

01:50:06.474 --> 01:50:08.267
<i>Lifts up</i>

01:50:08.310 --> 01:50:10.811
<i>From off your chest</i>

01:50:12.063 --> 01:50:15.733
