01:50:21.406 --> 01:50:25.242
<i>My love, I forgive you</i>

01:50:26.745 --> 01:50:30.998
<i>You never planned to die</i>

01:50:31.041 --> 01:50:35.294
<i>And love, I'll place two pennies</i>

